<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Réinitialisation de mot de passe</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f7; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #f4f4f7;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 20px;">
        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width: 480px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);">

          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 32px 24px 24px; background-color: #e0001a;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">
                Asernum - Auchan
              </h1>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 32px 32px 24px;">
              <h2 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a2e;">
                Réinitialisation de mot de passe
              </h2>
              <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 14px; color: #555770; line-height: 1.6;">
                Vous avez demandé la réinitialisation de votre mot de passe. Utilisez le code ci-dessous pour continuer :
              </p>

              <!-- OTP Code -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
                    <div style="display: inline-block; padding: 16px 40px; background-color: #f0f0f5; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e0e0ea;">
                      <span style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a2e; letter-spacing: 8px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;">
                        <%= otp %>
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #888898; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;">
                Ce code est valable <strong>5 minutes</strong>.
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #888898; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;">
                Si vous n'êtes pas à l'origine de cette demande, ignorez cet email.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px 32px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f5;">
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #aaaabc; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;">
                Asernum-job &mdash; Charles Désiré Bally
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
